text: Cheng Wentao (born 18 May 1998) is a Chinese synchronised swimmer. She participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning a medal. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese synchronized swimmers Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in synchronised swimming Category:Artistic swimmers at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships
